data.description: Welcome to the beautiful Trilby community. This home is located in a large Cul-de-sac it is a two story, 5 bedroom, 3 bathroom home has a bonus room AND a loft. Upon entering the 1st floor you will walk into the foyer that leads to the Great room and Dinning room combo. A few steps away is the Kitchen which was freshly painted in 2023, the microwave and garbage disposal was replaced in 2023. The remaining appliances were replaced in 2016. There is a bedroom and full bathroom just passed the living room. The laundry room is located at the bottom of the stairway, the washer and dryer was replaced in 2017. Once you head up the stairs you will walk into a loft area the leads to a large bonus room with French doors that can be used in so many ways, a theater, playroom, library, craft room, art studio or an in house gym. The primary suite has 2 walk in closets, large walk in shower and garden tub. The remaining 3 bedrooms a full bath are located on the opposite side of the home which creates a great split floor plan and allows for plenty of privacy. This home has been meticulously cared for throughout the years. HVAC replaced in 2022, exterior was painted in 2022 and ceiling fans installed throught the home. SELLER WILL CONTRIBUTE $5,000 TOWARDS BUYER'S CLOSING COSTS.
